subproject.description:
The three years project  will assist INAD to enhance its role as National demining operator through these three main outputs:
Increased management and technical cacapity of INAD at Headquarters level;
A dynamic and well supported Technical Demining School (ETD);
Seven of 15 INAD Demining Brigades trained and equipped and responding development needs.

